As of the [[2020 United States census]], there were 524 people, 217 households, and 142 families residing in the town.<ref>{{Cite web |title=S1101 Households and Families - 2020: Jay Town, Florida |url=https://data.census.gov/table?q=Jay+town;+Florida+&tid=ACSST5Y2020.S1101 |website=[[United States Census Bureau]] |access-date=February 20, 2024 |archive-date=September 5, 2024 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20240905085100/https://data.census.gov/table/ACSST5Y2020.S1101?q=Jay+town;+Florida+ |url-status=live }}</ref>

